products.content:
C IM NI BT

  • Thit k khung vin t titan chun hng khng v tr - Cc nh, bn cng vin cnh mng cm nm thoi miHiu nng Pro chin game th ga - Chip A17 Pro mang li hiu nng ha v cng sng ng v chn thcTho sc sng to v quay phim chuyn nghip - Cm 3 camera sau n 48MP v nhiu ch tin tinNt tc v mi gip nhanh chng kch hot tnh nng yu thch ca bn
iPhone 15 Pro Max thit k mi vi  cht liu titan chun hng khng v tr bn b, trng lng nh, ng thi trang b  nt Action v cng sc  USB-C tiu chun gip nng cao tc sc. Kh nng chp nh nh cao ca  iPhone 15 bn Pro Max n t  camera chnh 48MP, camera  UltraWide 12MP v camera telephoto c kh nng zoom quang hc n  5x. Bn cnh ,  iPhone 15 ProMax s dng chip  A17 Pro mi mnh m. Xem thm chi tit nhng im ni bt ca sn phm qua thng tin sau!

nh gi in thoi iPhone 15 Pro Max c g mi

iPhone 15 Pro Max em li mt din mo hon ton mi v s hu nhiu tnh nng u vit cng cng ngh tin tin. Hy khm ph cc nh gi chi tit v sn phm v kha cnh thit k, mn hnh, hiu nng, thi lng pin v b camera c o qua cc thng tin di y!

Hiu nng mnh m cng chipset A17 Pro tin tin 

Sn phm trang b  chip A17 Pro c sn xut trn  tin trnh 3nm, mang li bc ci tin t ph. Nh nhng ci tin v thit k v kin trc vi m, CPU mi  nhanh hn n 10%, h tr tnh nng nh Ging ni c nhn hay t ng sa li chuyn nghip. Khng ch vy,  GPU nhanh hn n 20% vi thit k 6 li mi nhm nng cao hiu sut v tit kim nng lng.

(nh: Apple.com)

iPhone 15 Pro c mt bc tin ng k vi cng ngh d tia tng tc phn cng, vi tc nhanh hn gp 4 ln so vi cc phin bn trc y dng cng ngh d tia da trn phn mm. Kt qu ca s ci tin ny l tri nghim ha trn thit b tr nn mt m hn, c bit l tri nghim khi chi game v s dng ng dng thc t o (AR) s tr nn sng ng hn. Ngi dng s c tri nghim chin game mt m hn vi: Resident Evil 4, Seadth Stranding, Resident Evil Village hay Assassin's Creed Mirage,...

(nh: Apple.com)

Chip A17 Pro c trang b mt b gii m AV1 c bit, gip nng cao cht lng video v tit kim pin khi bn s dng cc dch v truyn pht. ng thi, b iu khin USB mi c ci tin h tr tc USB 3 ln u xut hin trn iPhone, cung cp kh nng truyn d liu nhanh hn ng k v h tr u ra video vi phn gii HDR 4K tc 60 fps.

Cng ngh mn hnh vt tri

Mn hnh  OLED trn  iPhone 15 Pro Max l mt im c bit khng th b qua. Vi kch thc  6,7 inch cng phn gii nh cao  2796x1179 pixel, tn s qut 120Hz v mt im nh ln n 460 ppi, mn hnh mang n tri nghim n tng cho ngi dng. N cn c trang b cng ngh HDR, gip hin th mu sc v sng chn thc hn bao gi ht.

(nh: Apple.com)

Thm vo , cng ngh  TrueTone hin i c tch hp, t ng iu chnh mu sc ca mn hnh da trn mi trng xung quanh. Vi s kt hp ny, bn c th thy r rng rng mn hnh ca iPhone 15 Pro Max to ra tri nghim xem phim, chi game v lt web vt tri vi hnh nh sng ng, rc r, v mu sc chn thc.

Tnh nng Dynamic Island c o

D khng phi ln u xut hin trn iPhone, nhng vic Dynamic Island tip tc c trang b trn Apple iPhone 15 Pro Max vn p ng c nhu cu ca ngi dng. Dynamic Island mang n tri nghim th v, a dng tnh nng nh m nhc, xem maps m khng cn thot khi ng dng ang m. Bn cnh , vi tnh nng cp nht thng bo theo thi gian thc mang n tnh tin li khi s dng in thoi IP 15 Pro Max.

(nh: Apple.com)

Dung lng pin s dng thoi mi, cng kt ni USB-C

iPhone 15 Pro Max s hu vin pin c  dung lng ln hn ng k so vi th h trc . Vi vin pin ny, bn c th thng thc  video ln n 29 gi, xem video trc tuyn ln n 25 gi, nghe nhc ln n 95 gi (tu vo tc v khc nhau m thi gian c th thay i). Nh vy, bn c th thoi mi s dng c ngy m khng lo gin on gia chng.

(nh: Apple.com)

Thit b h tr sc Magsafe ln n 15W, sc khng dy Qi ln n  7.5W. Khi sc vi b tip hp ngun 20W hoc cng sut ln hn, iPhone 15 Pro Max c th sc y ln n 50% pin trong vng 30 pht.

im khc bit ca iPhone 15 Pro Max cn nm   cng sc USB-C mi, cho php s dng 1 cp sc np nng lng cho cc thit b khc nh Mac, iPad, AirPods Pro gen 2 c nng cp v iPhone 15 Pro Max. Ngoi ra, bn c th dng iPhone 15 Pro Max sc AirPods hoc Apple Watch thng qua cng USB Type C ny.

Kt ni mng 5G, cho tri nghim internet vt tri

iPhone 15 Pro Max c bit kh nng h tr kt ni 5G, mang n tri nghim internet nhanh v n nh hn bao gi ht. Do , bn c th tha sc xem video trc tuyn, chi game online, ti ni dung v thm ch lm vic t xa m khng lo gp s cn tr t tnh trng git lag. Ngoi ra, 5G cn gip bn truy cp internet nhng khu vc c tn hiu yu mt cch mt m.

Tch hp cng ngh eSIM tin li

Mt iu th v na iPhone 15 Pro Max l c th lu tr  ti a n 8 eSIM, c th bt ln s dng bt c lc no. Tuy nhin tu vo khu vc s dng m thit b ch c th s dng c 1 n 2 eSIM cng lc. Ngi dng c th kch hot eSIM ti trang web trc tuyn ca nh mng, hoc nh nhn vin h tr kch hot khi nhn my.

Nt tc v vi c ch mi tin li hn

Sn phm t  iPhone Pro Max 2023 cn c mt im mi l phm gt rung c thay i thnh  nt tc v (Action Button) vi c ch hon ton mi. Nhiu reviewer nh gi nt tc v trn IP 15 Pro Max rt mnh m, c th khi chy hu ht ng dng trn thit b nh: nt rung chung, ch tp trung, cc ng dng camera, n pin, ghi m, knh lp,... Ngoi ra cn c cc tr nng khc ngi dng tu chnh theo nhu cu s dng.

(nh: Apple.com

Thit k bn b cng cht liu titan cao cp

iPhone 15 Pro Max c ch to bi  cht liu titan cao cp  chun hng khng v tr vi bn n tng. Sn phm khng ch thu ht mi nh nhn bi din mo tinh t v hin i m cn mang n phin bn Pro nh nht tng c ca Apple. Khng ch vy, y l mt sn phm thn thin vi mi trng bi hng s dng nguyn liu ti ch gim lng rc thi.

(nh: Apple.com)

Cng ngh camera n tng, cho hnh nh chi tit chn thc nht

H thng  camera kp tin tin trn iPhone 15 Pro Max khng ch mang li nhng tri nghim quay chp n tng m cn bin mi khonh khc thnh mt tc phm ngh thut. Camera chnh  48MP, camera UltraWide  12MP vt tri vi kh nng ti u ha chp nh, mang n bc nh phn gii siu sc nt vi mu sc chn thc. 

(nh: Apple.com)

Ngi dng c th iu chnh vi 3 tu chn tiu c: 35mm, 28mm, 24mm v c th la chn 1 tiu c bt k ci t mc nh. Camera 48MP h tr hnh nh HEIF phn gii gp 4 ln.  iu ny cng vi kh nng x l hnh nh tin tin to ra nhng bc nh p v n tng hn.

(nh: Apple.com)

Camera telephoto 12MP cng mang n s ci thin ng k. N c kh nng thu phng quan hc phm vi ln n  5x, mang li s c o v chuyn nghip cho mi bc nh. Tnh nng thu phng quang hc h tr tt trong cc trng hp cn ghi li nhng khonh khc, hnh nh t xa, chp cn cnh. Module dch chuyn 3D t ng ly nt kt hp vi cng ngh cm bin chng rung quang hc l im ci tin c nh gi cao.

(nh: Apple.com)

Cng vi , cng ngh  Photonic Engine to nn sc mu ti sng, chn thc v ni bt cc chi tit. Ngoi ra, camera trc TrueDepth 12MP c kh nng t ng ly nt kt hp vi kh nng chp nh cn cnh v cht lng nhm, gip bn bt trn nhiu khonh khc qu gi.

iPhone 15 Pro Max c nh gi l mu smartphone selfie p nht

iPhone 15 Pro Max c trang b camera selfie vi phn gii 12MP, tng t nh 14 Pro Max tuy nhin my mang li kh nng chp nh selfie vt tri so vi th h trc. c bit, theo DxOMark, iPhone 15 Pro Max l mu smartphone cho kh nng chp selfie p nht t trc n nay. Vi 149 im, camera selfie trn thit b mang li kh nng chp selfie vi phi sng chnh xc.

(Ngun nh Apple.com)

Bn cnh , hnh nh c chi tit cao, trong qu trnh chp thit b cho kh nng ly nt nhanh chng. Bn cnh chp nh th DxOMark cng nh gi cao kh nng quay video trn thit b vi kh nng mang li video n nh, k c khi ngi dng di chuyn. iPhone 15 Pro Max c c kh nng quay chp so vi thit b tin nhim c th nh b x l tn hiu hnh nh (ISP) cng vi l con chip mi A17 Pro.

Cng ngh Face ID bo mt hng u

Vi cng ngh tin tin ca  Face ID tch hp trong iPhone 15 Pro Max, thao tc m kha thit b tr nn d dng v an ton hn bao gi ht. Sn phm ny s dng kh nng nhn din khun mt v cng chnh xc, ngay c trong cc iu kin nh sng bin i v cc gc khc nhau. H thng  camera TrueDepth m bo cho bn tri nghim m kha nhanh chng v bo mt cao.

(nh: Apple.com)

H iu hnh iOS 17 mi nht 2023

IOS 17 trn t iPhone 15 Pro Max mang n nhng ti u ng k v hiu nng, tnh bo mt v tri nghim trn thit b. Ngi dng c th s dng nhng tnh nng th v v giao din mt m. Phin bn cp nht h iu hnh ny cng c cho l ng cp nht trn thit b, k c cc dng iPhone 11, 12. Mt s tnh nng mi trn IOS 17 ca iP 15 Pro Max m bn nn th:

-  Namedrop ci tin hn Airdrop: ch cn t 2 chic iPhone cng h iu hnh IOS 17 truyn ti cc file d liu. Thao tc ny gip tit kim thi gian ng k so vi cch gi file truyn thng bng Airdrop.

-  Nhc chung mi: mt iu mi m c mang n l hng chc bi nhc chung mi tng thch cho c cuc gi v bo thc. Ngi dng c th tu chnh nhc chung cho tng eSIM phn bit cuc gi n t sim no mt cch hu ch.

-  T ng xo tin nhn OTP: nng cao tnh bo mt, IOS 17 cn c th t xo cc tin nhn vi m OTP c gi n sau khi ngi dng chn t ng in (autofill). Tuy nhin s dng bn cn thc hin ci t trc.

(nh: Apple.com)

-  nh i din lin h: ngi dng hon ton c th tu chnh nh i din cho cc lin h ca mnh, khin danh sch lin h tr nn sinh ng v d s dng hn.

-  To nhn dn ng: nhn dn ng c to t nh, video hoc live photo trn in thoi. Cc nhn dn ny c th c s dng cho tin nh, ghi ch v nh du. Vi nhn dn ng trn IOS 17, cc cuc tr chuyn s tr nn sinh ng v th v hn bao gi ht.

Kt ni vi h sinh thi Apple (Apple Watch, Airpods, Mac)

Mt im ni bt ca iPhone so vi cc thit b smartphone khc chnh l h sinh thi Apple. Theo , in thoi iPhone 15 Pro Max c th kt ni vi cc thit b khc trong cng h sinh thi nh Apple Watch, Airpods hay Mac mt cch nhanh chng. Theo :

- iPhone v Apple Watch: H tr kim tra tin nhn, tr li cuc gi hay iu khin cc ng dng trn iPhone mt cch tin li.

- iPhone v Mac: Chuyn i lin mch gia cc thit b qua tnh nng Handoff nh ngi dng c th thc hin cc cng vic cn dang d trn thit b khc. Cng vi , ngi dng c th truy cp vo cc d liu, hnh nh, video nh h thng iCloud ng b.

- iPhone v Airpods: Kt ni nhanh chng, h tr tr li cuc gi cng nh gi Siri trn di ng thng minh

(nh: Apple.com)

Tc ti xung nhanh hn ti 96% th h tin nhim

C 14 Pro Max v 15 Pro Max u c Apple trang b cng ngh wifi 6 v 5G (sub-6 GHz), tuy nhin tc truyn ti trn iPhone 15 Pro Max nhanh hn ti 96% so vi th h tin nhim. Theo , in thoi iPhone 15 Pro Max cho tc ti xung trung bnh 251,37 Mbps (khong 31,4 MB/s). Trong khi tc ti trn iPhone 14 Pro Max l 127,83 Mbps. (S liu tham kho t Ookla)

(Ngun nh Apple.com)

iPhone 15 Pro Max c bao nhiu mu, mua mu no p

Khng a dng mu sc nh trn 2 phin bn thng, iPhone 15 Pro s hu nhng gam mu trung tnh. C th  iPhone 15 Pro c bn mu sc l: Titan trng, titan en, titan xanh v titan t nhin. Trong :

Titan t nhin: y l mu sc hon ton mi cha tng c xut hin trc y trn cc thit b Apple. Mu sc ny kh tng ng vi mu bc pha xm nh kim vi kh nng phn chiu nh sng tt.

Titan trng: Khc vi nhng sc trng khc tng c xut hin, mu titan trng trn iPhone 15 Pro Max vi khung vin titan mang li mt v ngoi bng by hn. Sc trng trung tnh ny cng gip ngi dng d dng phi vi cc ph kin v trang phc khc nhau.

(nh: Apple.com)

Titan en: L s kt hp ca nh kim loi c trng trn cht liu titanium cng sc en huyn b nh mang li mt mu sc ti n gin nhng vn y sang trng v tinh t. Mu en trn th h iPhone mi ny c phn nht hn so vi nhng sc en trc ca cc thit b Apple.

Titan xanh: Sc xanh trn thit b c pha xm nh mang li s b n. So vi mu xanh lam tng xut hin trn iPhone 12 Pro th titan xanh ti hn v m hn.

Vy nn chn mu no khi mua iPhone 15 Pro Max. Ty thuc vo tnh cch v s thch ca ngi dng la chn c mu sc ph hp. Trong titan trng v titan en l hai tone mu d s dng v phi vi cc vt dng khc nht.

iPhone 15 Pro Max c bao nhiu phin bn b nh trong

V kh nng lu tr, in thoi iPhone 15 Pro Max c ba phin bn cu hnh b nh trong cho ngi dng la chn bao gm: 256GB, 512GB v 1TB. Vi mi phin bn s c kh nng lu tr khc nhau:

- 256GB: Lu tr khong 2300 bc nh nh dng JPG, 362 video phn gii 4k UHD (Hoc 1105 pht video FHD) v 1100 bi ht (C nn).

-  512GB: Lu tr c 2800 bc nh JPG v 2095 pht video FHD (Hoc 804 pht video 4K UHD), 1400 bi ht (C nn)

-  1TB: Lu tr 3200 nh nh dng JPG v 1600 bi ht (c nn), 894 pht video 4K UHD (hoc 2565 pht video FHD).

(Ngun nh Apple.com)

iPhone 15 Pro Max dung lng 256GB c dng khng?

Th h in thoi Apple mi 2023 ny, Apple loi b phin bn dung lng b nh trong 128GB. Theo , iPhone 15 Pro Max 256GB b nh trong s l phin bn b nh chun. Vy 256GB b nh lu tr c dng khng, ph hp s dng vi nhng ai?

256GB l dung lng lu tr ln, ph hp vi nhu cu s dng ca i a s ngi dng c bn. Theo , nu s dng in thoi trong cc nhu cu nh chi game, gi in, nhn tin, lt web th 256GB hon ton c th p ng c nhu cu. Tuy nhin, vi ngi dng thc hin cc cng vic v sng to ni dung, cn lu tr nhng hnh nh hay thc phim phn gii cao vi dung lng ln th c th cn nhc n nhng phin bn dung lng cao hn.

So snh iPhone 15 Pro Max v iPhone 14 Pro Max

iPhone 15 Pro Max tip ni nhiu im mnh t phin bn trc, iPhone 14, v c b sung, ci tin vi nhiu cng ngh tin tin mi. Hy cng xem qua bng  so snh iPhone 15 Pro Max vi iPhone 14 Pro Max di y nm r s tng ng v khc bit gia hai dng sn phm ny!

im khc bit ca iPhone 15 Pro Max vi 14 Pro Max nm   lp v c lm bng cht liu Titanium nh, bn b v cao cp, iu ny gip trng lng my gim i ng k. Thm vo , mt s im ni bt khc nh chip A17 Pro sn xut trn tin trnh 3nm cho hiu nng mnh m,  cng sc USB-C 3.0 vi tc nhanh hn v  camera zoom quang 5x. Mt im ng ch cn nm nt Action thay th cho nt gt tt ch im lng, v tr nm pha trn 2 nt tng gim m lng. K c trn phin bn  iPhone 15 128GB tiu chun, Apple cng p dng nhng thay i ny mang n tri nghim hon ho.

iPhone 15 Pro Max gi bao nhiu tin, bng gi chi tit?

iPhone 15 Pro Max ra mt cng series iPhone 15  thu ht s ch ca cng ng yu cng ngh trn ton cu khng ch bi s i mi v cng ngh m cn bi mc gi hp l. Vy in thoi  iPhone 15 Pro Max gi bao nhiu khi bt u m bn ti Vit Nam? Vi mc gi khi im  t 1.199 USD ti th trng M, ty thuc vo quc gia v cc yu t c th, gi sn phm c th thay i.

Vy iPhone 15 Pro Max gi bao nhiu ti Vit Nam - tham kho ngay bng gi chi tit sau:

V sao nn chn mua in thoi iPhone 15?

iPhone 15 Pro Max c cc tn cng ngh ch , c bit l cc iFan bi tnh t ph v cng ngh cng hiu nng vt tri. y xng ng l 1 trong nhng siu phm m bn nn s hu trong nm 2023.

Kh nng s dng bn b

Khng ch iPhone 15 Pro Max m cc sn phm khc ca Apple u c sn xut vi quy trnh nghim ngt v t cc chng nhn tiu chun quc t, m bo bn v kh nng s dng trong thi gian di. Khng ch vy, vi cht liu titan cao cp chun hng khng v tr, bn li cng yn tm trong qu trnh s dng.

(nh:Apple.com)

Kh nng bo mt, bo v d liu ngi dng cao

Sn phm tch hp Camera TrueDepth, mang li kh nng nhn din khun mt chnh xc ngay c trong cc gc v iu kin nh sng khc nhau. iu ny khng ch gip bn m kha thit b mt cch nhanh chng m cn bo v thng tin c nhn mt cch ti u.

Khng dng li , Camera TrueDepth cn l nn tng cho nhiu tnh nng bo mt v tin ch khc nh  Animoji, Memoji v ch chp nh chn dung cht lng cao vi hiu ng n tng. Tt c nhng iu ny u ng gp vo vic to ra mt mi trng an ton v bo mt cho d liu c nhn v thng tin quan trng ca bn trn thit b ny.

Hiu nng mnh m

Sn phm c trang b cng ngh tin tin v  chipset A17 Pro, mang li hiu sut nh cao cho mi nhu cu s dng ca bn.Kh nng x l nhanh chng v mt m gip bn d dng thc hin cc tc v a nhim, chi game yu thch, v lm vic vi ng dng nng. Khng ch vy, dung lng b nh ln c sn trn  iPhone 15 Pro Max cung cp khng gian lu tr ng k, m bo bn c ch lu tr d liu, hnh nh v video quan trng ca mnh.

(nh:Apple.com)

Nng cao tri nghim vi chnh sch bo hnh Apple

Sn phm iPhone thng c  bo hnh chnh hng 1 nm. iu ny ng ngha vi vic bn c th tn hng dch v kim tra v bo hnh t cc trung tm y quyn ca Apple trn khp c nc.

Chnh sch bo hnh ca Apple khng ch m bo s h tr k thut chuyn nghip m cn mang n s yn tm v vic s dng sn phm. Nu thit b ca bn gp li do nh sn xut hoc trong iu kin bo hnh, bn c th d dng a my n c kim tra v sa cha min ph hoc vi mc gi u i. iu ny gip nng cao gi tr ca chic iPhone 15 Pro Max v to s tin tng trong vic s dng sn phm.

Chuyn i d liu n gin

Ch cn mt vi thao tc n gin, bn c th chuyn i d liu quan trng nh tin nhn v hnh nh t cc thit b khc mt cch d dng. Khng cn phi lo lng v vic mt d liu quan trng hay rc ri trong qu trnh chuyn i. iu ny gip bn tit kim thi gian v cng sc, tn hng ngay tri nghim s dng mi m trn iPhone 15 ProMax.

(nh:Apple.com)

Ph kin a dng v tnh nng v mu sc

S a dng v ph kin l mt trong nhng im ng ch ca  iPhone 15 Pro Max. Bn c th tn hng s linh hot trong vic ty chnh thit b ca mnh theo cch ring bit. C nhiu loi p lng v bao da vi cc mu sc v kiu dng c o bo v thit b v th hin phong cch c nhn. Ngoi ra, cc ph kin nh tai nghe khng dy,  sc nhanh MagSafe, v nhiu sn phm khc cng gip nng cao tri nghim s dng.

(nh:Apple.com)

Sn phm thn thin mi trng

Apple s dng cc  vt liu ti ch v nguyn liu thn thin vi mi trng trong qu trnh sn xut iPhone 15 Pro Max. iu ny gip gim lng rc thi v tc ng n ti nguyn t nhin. Khng ch vy, sn phm cn tit kim nng lng trong qu trnh s dng hng ngy, gip gim lng kh nh knh.

Kt ni vi bn b cng h sinh thi

iPhone 15 Pro Max khng ch l mt chic in thoi thng minh, m cn l cu ni bn kt ni vi bn b v gia nh thng qua h sinh thi ca Apple. S tch hp mt m vi cc sn phm v dch v khc nhau gip bn thc hin cc hot ng chia s v giao tip mt cch d dng hn bao gi ht.

(nh:Apple.com)

Bn c th chia s nh, video v ti liu mt cch nhanh chng qua  iMessage v AirDrop. S dng  FaceTime  thc hin cuc gi video cht lng cao vi ngi thn v bn b, d h bt k u trn th gii. Ngoi ra, tch hp vi iCloud gip bn lu tr v truy cp d liu c nhn t bt k thit b no trong h sinh thi Apple.

Ti sao nn mua iPhone 15 Pro Max chnh hng ti CellphoneS?

s hu c sn phm  iPhone 15 ProMax chnh hng, gi tt, u i hp dn th vic tm kim n v uy tn v ng tin cy l iu v cng quan trng. Mt trong nhng h thng cung cp sn cng ngh chnh hng, gi tt hin nay l CellphoneS:

  • Sn phm chnh hng, c bo hnh y : CellphoneS l mt trong s t nhng chui bn l chnh hng Apple s hu chui trung tm bo hnh chnh hng u quyn Apple CARES.vn. Khch hng mua hng ti CellphoneS hon ton yn tm vi chnh sch bo hnh i mi 30 ngy u, bo hnh 12 thng tin li, nhanh chng ti cc trung tm bo hnh CARES.vn.
  • Thu c ln i vi tr gi hp dn: Chng trnh mang n tri nghim c o vi chng trnh thu c ln i v cng hp dn. Bn s c hng tr gi cao cho chic iPhone c ca mnh, gip gim ng k chi ph khi s hu iPhone 15 ProMax mi.
  • Gim gi su cho ph kin mua km chnh hng: Khi mua km ph kin ti ca hng cng vi chic iPhone 15 Pro Max, bn s c hng u i hp dn vi mc gim gi su. Nh vy, khch hng c th trang b cho chic in thoi mi ca mnh bng cc ph kin cht lng, nh p lng, tai nghe, hoc b sc khng dy vi mc tit kim ng k.
  • Tr gp 0%, tr trc ch vi 1 khon nh: CellphoneS trin khai chng trnh tr gp 0% vi mc tr trc thp gip khch hng gim bt p lc v gnh nng ti chnh. Ch cn chi tr 1 khon nht nh theo tng thng vi gi tr gp chn, bn c th tn hng ngay tin ch m sn phm mang li.
